title: Pilates Full Body Workout | Quick, Easy, & Effective in 15 MIN 🔥
description:
This effective 15 minute full body pilates workout is an entire body fitness class where you need no equipment & nothing more than yourself and a mat on the floor. 

Remember to do your best, and take breaks if needed... and come back as often as possible to redo the class and witness your improvements and strength increase first-hand!
